| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1507 — Recovery Inhibition (ALP-001)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 8adf77cc-ad02-5a35-87cc-1d0f313f19a8"
